SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[ColorId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageLocalPath], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SizeId], [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [s].[Id], [s].[RAM], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
